ActEnergy Efficiency Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the ENERGY EFFICIENCY REGULATIONS by raising the minimum energy-efficiency standards for both gas-fired and electric water heaters as well as for automatic clothes-washing machines designed for household use, and by introducing standards for electric exit signs and for water chillers used to cool large buildings.
